Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.40,0:00:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The War Game between the Freya Familia and\Nthe allied army is turning out to be pretty one-sided!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.16,0:00:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The allies' biggest hitter, Rabbit's Foot, \Nis currently getting steamrolled by the King, Ottarl!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.11,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Não há como deter a Familia mais poderosa de Orario!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.94,0:00:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas sério, eu acho que eles já provaram o suficiente!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.57,0:00:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Alguém pare esse espetáculo horrível!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.91,0:00:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Bell...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.95,0:00:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mestre Bell...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.51,0:02:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chifre... Eu detesto a maneira como você me imita.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Acabe logo com isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.86,0:02:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Vá dizer para Hedin que ele precisa \Nterminar o jogo da guerra agora!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.62,0:03:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lá vem problema!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A Familia de Freya vai para o ataque!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A squadron led by Vana Freya is\Nnow rushing towards the eastern side!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.92,0:03:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're invading the ruins\Nwhere the allies' Gods are hiding!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tem que correr, Senhora Hestia!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.14,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, você nos pegou!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nos rendemos!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.48,0:03:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Queremos ficar do lado da Senhora Freya! Entende?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.94,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Os deuses Magni e Modi estão ambos fora!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Seguidos rapidamente por Ogma, Serket e Sobek!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.45,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Os deuses aliados estão caindo como moscas!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.29,0:03:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai! Parece que Soma também foi encontrado!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.88,0:03:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Os membros da Familia de qualquer deus que tenha sido \Nderrotado não podem mais participar do Jogo de Guerra.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.01,0:03:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,O que significa que o exército aliado acabou de perder \Numa grande parte de suas forças!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.68,0:04:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As coisas já estavam ruins,\Nmas agora estão ainda piores!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.56,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Saia daqui, Hestia!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles vão te encontrar mais cedo ou mais tarde se você ficar parado!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.48,0:04:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Vá para o oeste! Vá para a linha de frente!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Perderemos todas as chances de vitória se eles te encontrarem!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, mas o que sobre você?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou acting como isca!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora vá embora,\Nenquanto Takemikazuchi ainda está os segurando!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Você vai ter que fazer melhor do que isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Encontrei um!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos ataquem ao mesmo tempo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pode me vencer com força bruta!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,E aí vai a deusa He
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.24,0:05:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Deus Takemikazuchi finalmente encontrou seu par!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.61,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Os deuses Dellingr e Ratri também estão fora.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.20,0:05:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,O poder de Vana Freya e \Ndos Einherjar é simplesmente esmagador!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sem mencionar sua velocidade!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.75,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the 46 Familia that comprised the allied army,\Nthere are now only four remaining!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.96,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat seems imminent if those \Nfour Gods can't keep their flowers safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,O jogo vai acabar!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.72,0:05:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Como você vai ficar nessa, exército aliado?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Como esperado.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.22,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Esta foi a conclusão natural quando se considera\Nquantas superioridade militar eles têm.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.52,0:05:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Significa que ainda não há razão para entrar em pânico.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O plano está pronto.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As preparações estão feitas.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.99,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All we need is one successful push to throw them\Noff balance, then the tables will turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.95,0:05:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}É impossível para alguém como eu \Ncompetir contra a mente afiada do Mestre Hedin.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.29,0:05:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Então tenho que considerar suas táticas,\Nestilo de luta e padrões de pensamento...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}e aproveitar qualquer vantagem que puder!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O Mestre Hedin está posicionado incrivelmente \Nperto da retaguarda deles...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.68,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meu Deus!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, aguente firme, Senhora Daphne!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Daphne!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A nossa vitória é inevitável.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.44,0:06:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No entanto, você resiste. Em uma empreitada infrutífera.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.69,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, eu ainda não estou morto.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daphne...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Cassandra! Cure-me!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Luz da Alma!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou me curando muito devagar...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.71,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Essa arma amaldiçoada sua... é mesmo um incômodo.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.75,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something peculiar about your body\Nand the way it's been weathering all my blows.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.09,0:06:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Laurus Coroa.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,É uma habilidade que aumenta minha resistência.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, I really hate using it \Nsince it makes my skin all hard and woody.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Apenas mais sofrimento que o Senhor Apollon me causou.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.64,0:06:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep this up and you'll devolve into\Na human-faced sapling that is bereft of speech.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.02,0:07:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To what end do you brave\Nthrough such hell and brimstone?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é fácil.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.99,0:07:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is to buy as much time as possible by keeping\Nfirst-class adventurers like you busy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.91,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I had everybody else\Nthrow themselves at you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,O que eu seria se não lutasse com unhas e dentes?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Como pode ser tão imprudente?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.75,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No entanto, também merece minha respeito.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Portanto... Eu vou acabar com você!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh não, Daphne!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.22,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cassandra... cure-me novamente...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Poupe suas forças! Eu cuidarei disso agora mesmo!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se mova.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.81,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will judge any attempt to cast magic\Nas further resistance and cut you both to pieces.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Só se você baixar suas armas e \Nse render.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.78,0:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore-o e cure-me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Corra.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou esperar 3 segundos.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Três, dois...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nos rendemos!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, poupe Daphne!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.13,0:08:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é burro.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora não há ninguém para nos enfrentar aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso consumiu mais do meu tempo do que eu havia previsto.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sinto muito.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu gostaria de não ser tão inútil.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não pude fazer nada para mudar o curso do destino.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.32,0:08:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,O vento...?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mas o vento soprará a nosso favor!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Por favor, pare."
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Já basta."
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.51,0:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Há quanto tempo não imploro misericórdia assim?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu não posso vencer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}É impossível para mim derrotar o Sr. Ottarl.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.69,0:09:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mas...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.23,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Salve-me! Sr. Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu fiz uma promessa.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.07,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uma promessa para salvá-la.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A menos que...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,eu derrote você...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.66,0:09:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Não posso alcançar a Senhora Freya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.08,0:09:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.25,0:09:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Não posso alcançar a Senhora Freya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,E não posso ver a Sra. Syr.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,você vai cair.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mande ver.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's blowing...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O Vento Furioso chegou!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vim me juntar à batalha.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Espero que estejam preparados, irmãos.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.09,0:10:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparados para quê, posso perguntar?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Para cair pela minha lâmina.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.68,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pouca chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- H-Holy smokes!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Inacreditável! O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.58,0:10:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Quem é esse aventureiro?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que eles precisavam de alguém para se apoiar!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.58,0:10:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, por favor. Essa piada já era velha!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.75,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum, eu pensei que o Vento Furioso \Nestava morto!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ela está me enfrentando golpe por golpe.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isso não é nada como quando \Nlutamos na Festa das Deusas!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.52,0:11:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Você ficou mais forte! Nível 6 de força!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas não há maneira de você ter subido 2 níveis!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.03,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,É possível!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mais do que possível!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu já lutou bastante.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Desde o dia que pôs fim à era sombria de Orario!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.49,0:11:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She has a long history of combat that's filled\Nwith outstanding accomplishments!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.08,0:11:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago, she was already\Ntop tier among all the level 4s.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.13,0:11:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hardly surprising she'd be\Nthe first person to achieve a double rank up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.51,0:11:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was powerless. I suffered miserable defeats\Nat the hands of both you and the King.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I had to change.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't just let things stand as they were.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Astrea and everyone gifted me this...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(1223,2224,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}the Alvs Justitia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By using its sharp blade,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vou declarar vitória desta vez!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cercai aquela Elfa, rapidamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Einherjar!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.44,0:12:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Heith! Você ousaria interferir em nosso duelo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.86,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Seu orgulho não é da minha conta.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sua Senhora deseja ter Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,E nossa missão é eliminar rapidamente\Nqualquer ameaça potencial que possa atrapalhar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou errado?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.37,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Às vezes, o combate individual não é uma opção\Nonde os guerreiros devem encontrar seu fim.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.17,0:12:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,, Apesar dessas circunstâncias lamentáveis,\Nnão há nada que possamos fazer senão amaldiçoar os Destinos.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou usar isso, Senhora Astrea.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponha um fim nela, Einherjar!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Astrea Record.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.57,0:13:20.03,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"Com a obrigação cumprida,\Nas balanças são equilibradas."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.03,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela está lançando um feitiço! Não deixe-a terminar!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.79,0:13:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Que diabos?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.79,0:13:32.50,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"Bastião da ordem, coroa da retidão,\Nluz da vitória."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.50,0:13:38.26,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"Em nome da Deusa, que os rastros das estrelas sejam gravados\Nnessa terra assim como eles rasgam os Céus."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma barreira?! Uma justiça estelar?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.98,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"A justiça é transmitida."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Agallis Arvesynth!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um encantamento de chama?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é impossível!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alise...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Escaravelha Harnel!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Essa mágica pertence a Alise Lovell!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.85,0:14:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que diabos você pode usá-la?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Minha jornada terminou.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Então fui me reunir com Senhora Astrea,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,para herdar o espírito de Alise e de todos os outros.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos embora, Alise.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.52,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Astrea Record.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.56,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}É um tipo de magia única dos Ryu que permite a ela\Nusar os feitiços de seus antigos companheiros.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.65,0:15:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Com meu íchor servindo como intermediário,\Nela se tornou a sucessora da marca de justiça de Alise.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mesmo que Ryu tenha mudado para outra Familia,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a ligação dela com aquelas garotas nunca desaparecerá.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O caminho justo em seus olhos agora \Né deter sua amiga.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.87,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}E levando isso em conta, eu desejo iluminar seu caminho\Npara o futuro com a luz das estrelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso? É magia de invocação?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela é igual à Elfa Mil?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.97,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, ela não invocou nada.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.97,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Esse é um milagre do Mundo Inferior\Nque ultrapassa a compreensão.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.06,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"A justiça é transmitida."
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Registro de Astrea".
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Em outras palavras, são as memórias das estrelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A Familia Astrea.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.78,0:16:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles estão realmente aqui. A Familia Astrea retornou!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.66,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode fazer isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.54,0:16:19.88,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"Agora no céu da floresta distante,"
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.88,0:16:23.38,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"até às estrelas infinitas montadas \Nno firmamento eterno da noite."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.38,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Canto concorrente?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare ela!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.09,0:16:30.09,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"This fool doth entreat just once for\Nthe divine protection of the stars' fire."
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.64,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"Grant thy benevolent light to\Nthe one who abandoned thee!"
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Diabos, ela é boa em lançar feitiços!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.65,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"Apareça, vento errante... meu companheiro vagante!"
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.03,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"Cruze os céus, passe pelas terras desoladas!"
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.78,Default,italics?,0,0,0,,"Corra mais rápido do que qualquer outro!"
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Formidable.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Inacreditável! O que eu estou vendo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.70,0:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let the light of stardust occupy me\Nand strike my enemy!"
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Vento Luminoso!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Esquive-se!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.47,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,De quem é esse feitiço?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser... é Lady Ryu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu. Eu sabia que você viria.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma explosão?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sra. Ryu...?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the only one still standing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.08,0:17:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You amplified the scope of your spell\Nto make a wide-range attack.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.45,0:17:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It expunged the interlopers and\Ncleared the battlefield of obstacles.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isso me leva a supor que sua verdadeira intenção é...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.34,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Traga isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é louco!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lento! Fraco! Embotado!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.69,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Essa chama encantada é bastante intimidante,\Nmas eu já sei como contra-atacar!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.32,0:18:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Desde que o Vento Galeiro não dominou seu controle \Ndas chamas, minha melhor chance é... avançar!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Vá em frente e use as chamas dos seus amigos como armadura!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.95,0:18:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Não será suficiente para queimar meu Abismo Vítima!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.50,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que você tenha sofrido duas derrotas \Nnão significa que não possa acontecer três vezes, seu filhote!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.42,0:18:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Você ainda nem chegou aos meus pés!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.27,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Estou sendo impedido?! Como é isso possível?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.98,0:18:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não, deveria ser impossível eu perder!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Não esqueça que isto é um Jogo de Guerra.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.82,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Diga-me, quantos aventureiros você cortou \Ncom essa lâmina antes de lutar contra mim?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.37,0:18:59.70,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Preciso de um favor, pessoal.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.87,0:19:01.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Vão se ferrar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.58,0:19:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Inconcebível!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.37,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Armas amaldiçoadas podem conceder seu usuário \Ncom poder imenso, mas isso vem a um custo.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.21,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Principalmente uma queda nas estatísticas,\Ne alto consumo de stamina!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.55,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os guerreiros caídos aqui \Ntiraram suas forças!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.76,0:19:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Forçaram você a desperdiçar \Ntoda a sua energia quanto puderam!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridículo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Está tudo se juntando...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo está se juntando!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.44,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dama Daphne, Dama Tsubaki, Mestre Ouka, todos!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os sacrifícios que eles fizeram\Npara continuar lutando estão dando certo agora!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.08,0:19:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Não posso ter certeza de quem venceria em um verdadeiro duelo.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas agora?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.67,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Esta batalha é {\i1}nossa{\i1} para vencer!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alise Lovell.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.55,0:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seus flames de justiça... eram algo que eu admirava...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Arvelia!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.69,0:20:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é um a menos!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.73,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dainsleif foi derrotado!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim! Agora isso é mais como deve ser!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles fizeram isso! Eles derrotaram um!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles varreram o chão com Dainsleif!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.20,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue assim, Liliruca Arde!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Como gostaram disso, idiotas!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.63,0:20:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é enorme! Uhu!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomamos um aventureiro de primeira classe!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ainda somos isso! Agora as coisas podem virar!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Os aventureiros de primeira classe \Ntêm um grande impacto em uma Guerra de Jogos!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.05,0:20:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Suas forças deveriam começar a fraquejar depois de perder um!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Então a cadeia de comando desmorona\Ne o campo de batalha vira em caos!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.56,0:20:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,É uma rachadura na armadura deles! Nossa chance de vencer!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles bateram no Lorde Hogni?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.73,0:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,O que devemos fazer agora?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Parem de entrar em pânico!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Somos os Andhrímnir.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.24,0:21:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many of our people fall,\Nwe simply heal their wounds, slap them awake,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.91,0:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Enviar eles de volta para o campo de batalha!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.62,0:21:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Over and over! For as long as it takes!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu mesmo tratarei Lorde Hogni.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.12,0:21:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,O resto de vocês revivam os Einherjar!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.46,0:21:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim senhora!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Malditos sejam, exército aliado!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mas Lorde Hogni é o único que você conseguiu vencer.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.80,0:21:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}E com nossa mágica de cura,\Nele estará de pé em um piscar de olhos.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não deixarei você virar a mesa contra nós.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu esmagarei qualquer esperança que você tenha.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.89,0:21:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tudo pela Senhora Freya!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.31,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our victory is still assured!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.40,0:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.58,0:21:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,O que?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lute para sempre, meus guerreiros imortais de relâmpago.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.67,0:21:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Caelus Hildr!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.89,0:23:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Próxima vez: "Vingança"
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.96,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,opsync,"Olá, eu sou Bell Cranel da Familia Hestia."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.93,0:22:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,edsync,"Olá, eu sou Bell Cranel da Familia Hestia."
